Privacy Policy
InProfile
Welcome to InProfile, a Free app developed by us. InProfile offers this service without any charges and is designed for your use as it is.
This page informs you about our approach to collecting, using, and revealing Personal Information when you choose to utilize our Service.
By opting to use our Service, you consent to the collection and utilization of information as described in this policy. We collect Personal Information to enhance and refine the Service, and we will only share or use your data as outlined in this Privacy Policy.
The terms used in this Privacy Policy carry the same meanings as those in our Terms and Conditions, accessible on the InProfile platform unless specifically redefined in this Privacy Policy.
Information Collection and Use
To provide you with an enhanced experience, we might require you to provide us with specific personally identifiable information while using our Service. The information we ask for will be retained and utilized as outlined in this privacy policy.
Please be aware that the app uses third-party services that may gather information for identification purposes.
For your convenience, here are the links to the privacy policies of the third-party service providers employed by the app:
